News.Title: Tara Chand Infralogistic Solutions Q3 Results
News.Summary: Tara Chand Infralogistic Solutions reported flat net profit of ₹52 million in Q3, maintaining same level as previous year with zero growth.

News.Summary: Tara Chand Infralogistic Solutions has secured a significant contract worth ₹276.50 million, marking a major business development for the diversified company.

News.Summary: Tara Chand Infralogistics Solutions has secured a significant contract worth ₹241.4 million, marking a major business development for the diversified company.

News.Title: Tara Chand Infralogistic Solutions Reports Higher Q2 Profit and Revenue
News.Summary: Tara Chand Infralogistic Solutions reported net profit of 75 million rupees in Q2, up from 72 million rupees in the same quarter last year. The company's revenue increased to 750 million rupees from 658 million rupees year-over-year.

News.Summary: Tara Chand Infralogistic Solutions has secured domestic orders worth ₹58.76 crores for advanced machinery and skilled workforce from private firms.

News.Title: Tara Chand Infralogistic Solutions Secures ₹81.51 Crore Contract
News.Summary: Tara Chand Infralogistic Solutions has secured a contract valued at ₹81.51 crore. No further details about the nature of the contract or the client were provided in the given news snippet.

News.Title: Tara Chand Approves Land Purchase for Construction Equipment Depot
News.Summary: Tara Chand has approved an agreement to purchase land valued at 9 crore rupees. The land will be used to establish a construction equipment depot and for specialized service contracts.
